Package org.ejvm.compilation

The compilation package contains classes important for the compilation of eJVM programs, most notably the implementation of the eJVM compiler itself.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EjvmCompiler
    The EjvmCompiler provides methods to compile eJVM source code into an eJVM Executable File.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    EjvmCompilationException.Reason
    This enum contains all reasons why an EjvmCompilationException may have been thrown.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    EjvmCompilationException
    Exception class to be thrown when the EjvmCompiler encounters erroneous code during compilation, such as references to undefined variables.

Package org.ejvm.compilation Description
